{"analytics_identifier":"OT1427","base_path":"/government/organisations/race-equality-unit","content_id":"35616375-9be7-498b-a707-5b62391aa700","description":"We work across government and beyond to identify and tackle racial and ethnic inequalities – through legislation, policy and data. REU is part of the Cabinet Office and the Office for Equality and Opportunity .","details":{"acronym":"REU","alternative_format_contact_email":"accessible.formats@cabinetoffice.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>We work across government and beyond to identify and tackle racial and ethnic inequalities – through legislation, policy and data.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Race Equality Unit\">REU</abbr> is part of the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/cabinet-office\">Cabinet Office</a> and the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/office-for-equality-and-opportunity\">Office for Equality and Opportunity</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"cabinet-office","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Race<br/>Equality<br/>Unit"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/race-equality-unit/about/accessible-documents-policy","title":"Accessible documents policy"},{"href":"/government/organisations/race-equality-unit/about/media-enquiries","title":"Media enquiries"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/office-for-equality-and-opportunity-to-break-down-barriers-to-opportunity","image":{"alt_text":"image showing the Office for Equality and Opportunity's 7 ministers","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6708f72e080bdf716392f201/s712_OEO_Rebrand_PN_-_960_x_640.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6708f72e30536cb927483036/s465_OEO_Rebrand_PN_-_960_x_640.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6708f72e366f494ab2e7b720/OEO_Rebrand_PN_-_960_x_640.png"},"publ