","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-07-08T09:51:54Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Bridget Phillipson MP - Minister for Women and Equalities","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"60635c88-2518-493e-9b82-a0d776017796","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":1,"started_on":"2024-07-05T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/secretary-of-state-for-education","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/secretary-of-state-for-education","base_path":"/government/ministers/secretary-of-state-for-education","content_id":"845e63b4-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Secretary of State is responsible for the work of the Department for Education, including:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>early years and childcare</li>\n  <li>children’s social care</li>\n  <li>teacher quality, recruitment and retention</li>\n  <li>the school curriculum</li>\n  <li>school improvement</li>\n  <li>academies and free schools</li>\n  <li>further education</li>\n  <li>apprenticeships and skills</li>\n  <li>higher education</li>\n</ul>\n\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":13,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-11-08T09:31:05Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Secretary of State for Education","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/secretary-of-state-for-education","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-07-05T16:16:25Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Bridget Phillipson MP - Secretary of State for Education","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-07-22T15:22:19Z","schema_name":"person","title":"The Rt Hon Bridget Phillipson MP","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/bridget-phillipson","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/jacqui-smith","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/jacqui-smith","base_path":"/government/people/jacqui-smith","content_id":"8d7c6906-f1dd-4a7d-ba70-ecd1a08aefe6","details":{"image":{"alt_text":"The Rt Hon Baroness Smith of Malvern","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/669551bfa3c2a28abb50cfe8/s465_Jacqui_Smith_960x640.jpg"},"privy_counsellor":true},"document_type":"person","links":{"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"33e1de69-b71e-4022-9455-599511a2c01d","details":{"current":false,"ended_on":"2025-03-04T00:00:00+00:00","person_appointment_order":2,"started_on":"2024-10-08T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/government-spokesperson-for-equalities","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/government-spokesperson-for-equalities","base_path":"/government/ministers/government-spokesperson-for-equalities","content_id":"8cbdd1d2-93d5-4383-8cf6-92d7b01a84f4","details":{"body":"<p>Lords spokesperson on equalities.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":100,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-10-31T17:41:36Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Government spokesperson for Equalities","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/government-spokesperson-for-equalities","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-03-05T14:30:26Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"The Rt Hon Baroness Smith of Malvern - Government spokesperson for Equalities","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"6aeb8f43-444e-4659-92b2-9715ec47c517","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":3,"started_on":"2025-03-04T00:00:00+00:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/minister-for-women-and-equalities--4","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/minister-for-women-and-equalities--4","base_path":"/government/ministers/minister-for-women-and-equalities--4","content_id":"7cf56213-ff28-40f2-91f0-d224f643b06d","details":{"body":"<p>The minister’s responsibilities include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>lead policy responsibility for gender equality and women’s rights</li>\n  <li>sponsorship of the Equality and Human Rights Commission (EHRC) and Social Mobility Commission (SMC)</li>\n  <li>UK equality framework (including the Equality Act)</li>\n  <li>equality data and analysis</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The minister also has lead responsibility in the House of Lords on the following policy areas:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>socioeconomic opportunity</li>\n  <li>race and ethnicity policy</li>\n  <li>Employment Rights Bill (Department for Business and Trade lead)</li>\n</ul>\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":5,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-12-05T16:50:56Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Minister of State (Minister for Women and Equalities)","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/minister-for-women-and-equalities--4","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-03-05T11:30:16Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"The Rt Hon Baroness Smith of Malvern - Minister of State (Minister for Women and Equalities)","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"9e04f1b9-8abc-4a0a-9f31-2b78e1950f5b","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":1,"started_on":"2024-07-06T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/minister-of-state--175","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/minister-of-state--175","base_path":"/government/ministers/minister-of-state--175","content_id":"5dc89f34-86e1-4173-9980-0a525d4ef2f3","details":{"body":"<p>The minister’s Department for Education (DfE) responsibilities include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>governance, intervention and accountability of further education colleges</li>\n  <li>funding for education and training, provision and outcomes for 16- to 19-year-olds</li>\n  <li>further education financial stability and workforce</li>\n  <li>access to higher education, participation and lifelong learning entitlement</li>\n  <li>quality of higher education and the student experience (including the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.officeforstudents.org.uk/\">Office for Students</a>)</li>\n  <li>student finance (including the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/student-loans-company\">Student Loans Company</a>)</li>\n  <li>technical and vocational qualifications (level 3 and below), including T Levels</li>\n  <li>higher technical education (levels 4 and 5)</li>\n  <li>careers advice</li>\n  <li>support for young people aged 16 to 19 not in employment, education or training (NEET)</li>\n  <li>skills strategy and delivery</li>\n  <li>technical excellence colleges</li>\n  <li>international education</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The minister’s Department for Work and Pensions (DWP) responsibilities include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/skills-england\">Skills England</a> and Industry Training Boards</li>\n  <li>adult education, including basic skills</li>\n  <li>apprenticeships, including the growth and skills levy</li>\n  <li>skills bootcamps</li>\n  <li>sector skills packages</li>\n  <li>careers advice and support for young people over the age of 19 not in employment, education or training (NEET)</li>\n  <li>Youth Guarantee</li>\n</ul>\n\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":100,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-05-15T17:15:41Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Minister of State (Minister for Skills)","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/minister-of-state--175","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-07-06T21:04:35Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"The Rt Hon Jacqui 